/-
natural language description:

тАв Takes a ProjectivePoint with coordinates (X, Y, Z) and returns a CompletedPoint that results
from adding the input point to itself via elliptic curve point addition. Arithmetics are
performed in the field ЁЭФ╜_p where p = 2^255 - 19.

natural language specs:

тАв The function always succeeds (no panic)
тАв Given input point (X, Y, Z), the output CompletedPoint (X', Y', Z', T') satisfies:
- X' тЙб 2XY (mod p)
- Y' тЙб Y┬▓ + X┬▓ (mod p)
- Z' тЙб Y┬▓ - X┬▓ (mod p)
- T' тЙб 2Z┬▓ - Y┬▓ + X┬▓ (mod p)
-/

